{"tid":851571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港足新帥GW: 正聯絡一些合資格代表香港但暫未為港人熟悉的海外球員","createTime":"2018-10-07T09:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T16:58:52.000Z","uid":9030,"like":48,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2e362ad4fdc3a42608f08d098474862b9dd0c2c9","tid":851571,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"韋特過往執教關島及台灣時，不時召入一些在外地落班、卻具代表隊資格的球員，他指出香港其實也有如此兵源，「我們正在主動聯絡一些合資格代表香港的海外球員，也許很多人都不認識他們，但他們很快就會為人知。這批球員正在水平不俗的聯賽作賽，我們不會立刻就作徵召，這是較為長遠的事」。他表示暫不會透露這批球員的名字，「我不想為他們帶來麻煩，也不想令我們的計劃受阻，但他們都因為在港出生，或是父母在港出生而合資格，這種球員的數目，其實多得驚人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1945087/org/063564a5f727b9da4ce4209b632e7c21.jpg/bYJbdyEki9v4mwaqM2jcNqyuSC6vBndn0a72u9Gu9rs?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1945087%2Forg%2F063564a5f727b9da4ce4209b632e7c21.jpg%2FbYJbdyEki9v4mwaqM2jcNqyuSC6vBndn0a72u9Gu9rs%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=692f6c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f9f5484901aac5fe15a1fe661fe311fa116006f","tid":851571,"uid":9030,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這種球員的數目，其實多得驚人"},{"pid":"2e3c687a0ad27b331a81e6f87bb1bdec198cccc1","tid":851571,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"玩呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e475ec6f07823eb794f946df23c57385d26a34","tid":851571,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"咁都畀佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a